{"tid":210592,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（古法？）醉駕司機路邊食草20mins，想沖淡陣酒氣","createTime":"2017-04-21T05:22:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-21T05:28:52.000Z","uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"05d91f9c5b19bc15f541d4dde6f846d36dc85388","tid":210592,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T05:22:00.000Z","msg":"事發周一（17日）晚上11時許。&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n交警多次要求男子接受酒精吹氣檢測。但該名男子卻不斷說着：「我沒喝酒！我沒開車！」拒絕吹氣企圖拖延時間，隨後還發起酒瘋，抓起了路邊的草就往嘴裏塞，嚼來嚼去，有的吐掉，有的吃掉。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n男子的異常舉動，吸引路人圍觀，這一吃又過了20分鐘，甚至把周圍半米內的草都吃個精光。<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;「見過有人嚼口香糖、喝水，但吃草的，還是第一次。」在場警員說，馬大概以為吃草可以沖淡酒氣，好讓檢測時酒精含量更低。最終，在醫院裏，馬被驗出酒精含量為134mg/100ml，涉嫌因醉酒駕駛被捕。"},{"pid":"2a2fc229f4e54f28b61e7a9886d09a4ac7e03435","tid":210592,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T05:22:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170420/large/1492702042_e710.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170420%2Flarge%2F1492702042_e710.jpg&h=013a8e04&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e8c306eba62b69c749516e7b5d29949a5f8f10e9","tid":210592,"uid":39463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T05:23:47.000Z","msg":"馬食草，好合理呀"},{"pid":"6dac23d8af77ac997ffa9b172e416ea4a72b7f34","tid":210592,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T05:28:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>馬食草，好合理呀</blockquote><br />\n人點食得落？"}]}